ASSIGNMA      VACUUM      R_VOID
*MAT-PROP, ,%(rho)s, ,POLYETHY, POLYETHY, , ,

#ifdef USE_SPHERE
ASSIGNMA    POLYETHY R_IN_MOD
*ASSIGNMA    PET R_IN_MOD
